description: [``botocore``] This release introduces the SearchSampleQueries API that allows users to search for CloudTrail Lake sample queries.
[``botocore``] Adds support for UpdateStrategies in EKS Managed Node Groups.
[``botocore``] Added new authorization strategy value 'SMART_ON_FHIR' for CreateFHIRDatastore API to support Smart App 2.0
[``botocore``] Systems Manager doc-only update for January, 2025.
[``botocore``] Added CustomDirectories as a new directory option for storing inbound AS2 messages, MDN files and Status files.
